            "notes": "This deck focuses on utilizing aggressive creatures and combat tricks to quickly overwhelm the opponent and deal damage efficiently. Tifa Lockhart serves as the commander, providing a consistent source of damage and optimization for the deck's strategy. With a mix of powerful creatures like Mossborn Hydra and Surrak, Elusive Hunter, along with pump spells like Might of Old Krosa and Berserk, the deck aims to put pressure on the opponent early and often. Mana acceleration from cards like Llanowar Elves and Fyndhorn Elves allows for explosive plays and ensures the deck can keep up its aggressive pace. The land base is optimized for consistent mana production and includes utility lands to support the deck's overall game plan."
